posting_body: ['1 BR - $1025 - Sept 1st - 2308 Lyndale Ave S - Pet Friendly!!', 'This well-maintained property has a updated one bedroom for Sept 1st Move in!', 'Great access to the U of MN, Lots of public transportation a few feet from building.', 'Grocery, liquor store and coffee shops on same block.', 'Great access for walking to parks and Lakes!', 'The unit is 650 sq feet, update with tiled backsplash, updated appliances and dishwasher.', 'Microwave available if needed.', 'The bathroom has been updated, and ceramic tiled kitchen and entry way.', 'Large bedroom closet.', ' Unit is just a few feet from Updated laundry too.', 'Rent includes Heat, water, trash, you pay electric and internet.', 'US Internet available in building.', 'Controlled entry and on line resident portal for rent payments and maintenance requests.', 'Pet friendly building!', 'Pet rent $35 per month plus a one time pet fee of $300 required.', 'Dogs and cats ok, dogs up to 50 lbs ok.', 'Limit two pets.', 'Call today to schedule a showing!!', 'Deposit $700 with good credit!', 'Smoke free building.', 'Check out our reviews!', 'Nancy@', 'show contact info', 'Contact us today at:', 'nancy @ putnamproperties .', 'net', '<URL>', '<URL>', 'Visit <URL> for more info!', 'Sending a message via email (without explicit reply) does not mean an appointment for a showing has been scheduled.', 'Call to confirm an appointment for a showing.']
